 committee board committees encanas board of directors has five standing committees to examine and make recommendations on a variety of specific issues the board of directors approves the mandate for each committee outlining the responsibilities of the committee and the limits to its authority mandates are regularly reviewed and updated by the board the board of directors appoints board members to each respective committee including a committee chair board members selected for a specific committee typically have significant expertise and experience relevant to that committee board members serve on one or more of the following five committees audit committee corporate responsibility environment health and safety committee human resources and compensation committee nominating and corporate governance committee reserves committee committee membership chart how we select our board members board orientation and continuing education eca stock price tsx  can  nyse  usd  as of   minimum  minute delay privacy policy legal notice about this site site map glossary contact us copyright   encana corporation all rights reserved find us on facebook on twitter on linkedin on youtube on our rss feed board of directors  selection  encana corporation about us strategy resource play hub encanas values joint ventures leadership board  governance selection process orientation  continuing education board member biographies board committees mandates  guidelines documents  filings policies  practices ethos our history awards  recognition operations montney duvernay permian eagle ford do business with us contractor connection safety isnetworld drive safe safe  pressure and pipe principles courtesy matters a canadian landowner’s guide to pipelines expectations  practices material safety data sheets transportation of dangerous goods encana sarps sunset prairie lodge contracts  agreements invoicing land negotiation contacts us interest owner relations marketing encana operated roads our stories